= FSNET =

The aim of the FSNET (Firm Social Network) project is to procure to a firm an internal social network.


= Details =

The FSNET project is developed by the Master Pro students from the Artois University as a 5th year university project in collaboration with SQL Technology. The Study of the project were achieved by the Master students (4th year), the master pro are implementing the code.
